'''巴哈馬菁英賽'''為[[LPGA巡迴賽|LPGA巡迴賽]]其中的一項女子職業高爾夫賽事。首屆賽事於2013年5月在[[巴哈馬|巴哈馬]][[天堂島|天堂島]]的海洋俱樂部高爾夫球場舉行。首屆冠軍由[[李日姬|李日姬]]奪得，她以兩桿的成績擊敗[[趙艾潤|趙艾潤]]。<ref name=fnlldrbd>{{cite web|url=http://espn.go.com/golf/story/_/id/9314231/ilhee-lee-wins-bahamas-lpga-classic-first-lpga-tour-victory|publisher=Associated Press|title=Ilhee Lee wins 1st LPGA Tour event|date=May 27, 2013|accessdate=May 30, 2013|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304093708/http://espn.go.com/golf/story/_/id/9314231/ilhee-lee-wins-bahamas-lpga-classic-first-lpga-tour-victory|dead-url=no}}</ref>

